Class BeaconInfoSettings

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.estimote.sdk.cloud.model.BeaconInfoSettings
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class BeaconInfoSettings
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    Immutable representation of beacon's settings stored in Estimote Cloud. If you want to mutate your can use BeaconInfoSettings.Builder object or invoke builder() on existing object.
